      <dc:title>Handwritten postcard from Jonas to Jeanette Schenker, dated February 17,
        1938</dc:title>

      <dcterms:created>1938-02-17T12:00:00Z</dcterms:created>
      <dcterms:dateSubmitted>2015-12-07</dcterms:dateSubmitted>
      <dc:description>Jonas reports on a meeting at UE re: the prospects for a proposed Schenker
        edition series and an English translation, and for prospects in the USA.</dc:description>
